title: Conan the Usurper by Robert E. Howard
description:
Another of the de Camp Lancer Conan books.


This includes :-

"Introduction" (L. Sprague de Camp)
"The Treasure of Tranicos" (Robert E. Howard and L. Sprague de Camp)
"Wolves Beyond the Border" (Robert E. Howard and L. Sprague de Camp)
"The Phoenix on the Sword" (Robert E. Howard)
"The Scarlet Citadel" (Robert E. Howard)

With de Camp's editorial hand throughout, and, in fact, his creation/finishing of the first two stories.
